            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Deo P<supplied reason="lost">atrio</supplied> <lb n="2"/>Soli Ela<supplied reason="lost">gabalo</supplied> <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>G</abbr><ex>aius</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Iul</abbr><ex>ius</ex></expan> Av<supplied reason="lost">itus</supplied> <lb n="4"/>Alexi<supplied reason="lost">anus</supplied> <lb n="5"/>soda<supplied reason="lost">lis</supplied> <lb n="6"/>Titia<supplied reason="lost">lis</supplied> <lb n="7"/><expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>atus</ex></expan> Au<supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>g</abbr><ex>usti</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>ro</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>raetore</ex></expan></supplied> <lb n="8"/><expan><abbr>prov</abbr><ex>inciae</ex></expan> <supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>Raet</abbr><ex>iae</ex></expan></supplied>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Drei Fragmente eines Altars mit Bekrönung. Auf der linken Nebenseite Darstellung eines Baumes, auf der Rückseite Gittermuster. (B): Schillinger-Häfele: Z. 6: Titi[alis]; AE 1962; Radnóti: Z. 5/6: soda[l(is) ---] / Titia[l(is) ---]; Z. 7: lega[tus Aug. pr. pr.; Z. 8: prov[inciae Raetiae].</p>
            </div>
